			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1156">Oggok</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>The Stein Of Moggok Quest</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    The Stein Of Moggok Quest</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=47086"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Omlet of the Xegony</a> | 
		                        1/7/2000 1:26:36 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">This is a very long, hard quest and usable only by enchanters.  Ok if your a dark elf, you need a illusion like gnome or half-elf.  If your any other enchanter you must have Dark elf form and all must have the spell alliance.  Ok i suggest you bring with you 20 food and water just in case.  To start off have someone bind you to the docks at east freeport.  Then venture off to kithicor woods.  Once there head for rivervale if your a dark elf, cast invisibility.  Enter and find a spot with no guards.  Quickly cast half elf form and your safe for now.  Now go to misty thickett.  Before you do, if your a de (dark elf) cast invisibility and head through.  Once you arrive  find a spot FAR away from the guards and cast the illusion. Now you have 2 choices: either pay a newbie big bucks to bring you 2 honeycomb or hunt yourself.  The latter is rather easy since bixies, the ones carrying the comb, are level one or 2.  After that, return to rivervale and find the lady who will make you the honeyjumm in exchange for 30 gold and 2 honeycomb--i cant remember her name.  Get ready to do some walking!  Now head to queynos or get a tp to toxullia forest (more on that in a minute). Once you arrive to Queynos wait atr the docks for the boat (dont forget the illusion!) Once in Erudin find the lady who says something about a tonic and she will ask you to bring her something.  Do that and you get the second item.  If you tped to toxullia forest ask someone to take you to Erudin and do the tonic miniquest.  Now take the boat back to Queynos and find the temple oof light.  You will find a small pond in the center.  Target a fish in the pond and quickly jump in kill the fish loot its corpse and gate back to the docks in freeport where you were last bound WITHOUT leaving the water.  Now hop on a boat to the ocean of tears and buy several kiola nuts and gate back to the docks.  Now on the docks staring at the ocean, turn to your right and follow the docks until you come to a building.  Enter it and hail everyone to see if anyone says something about a recipe or a book give that person the honeyjumm a kiola nut the fish corpse and the tonic ALL at once and hell give you the recipe book.  Now head to Oggok. Follow the path and pass the huge building that has 3 entrances and pass the pod and in this building youll find clurg. Now YOU MUST ALLIANCE HIM OR YOU WONT GET THE STEIN!!! DO it twice to be safe and give him the recipe book and you get  the stein!! Now a little note the stein sells for about 300pp and it takes about 3hrs without teleports or sow.  I hope this guide helped  
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
