			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here is what you need to know about the NPC's and items. Kizzie Mintopp is the halfling that you need to give 3 honey combs to and you'll recieve the Honey Jum. When you get to Erudin, go to the BlueHawk and buy an Innoruuk's Kiss of Death, take this to the Erudin Library, at the top floor their is a female Erudite named Sinnkin Highbrow, give it to her and you'll recieve Erud's Tonic. Then catch a boat ride to Qeynos and kill a fish in the pond in the Temple of Life (bad faction hit.) You can purchase a Kiola Nut at the shop closest to the dock in the Ocean of Tears. (The merchants are woodelves so be careful about which illusion you choose.) After you get all four items, go to the bar in East Freeport near the docks, talk to Gregor Nasin, give him the items and he'll give you a recipe book. Take it to Clurg in Oggok (I did use Alliance twice just to be safe) and you'll get the Stein of Moggok. My main character is a wizard but I used my 8th lvl enchanter. Good luck...<BR>
<BR>
Ravenlok Von'Croft<BR>
<BR>
25th lvl Wizard
