			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok I've done it and I know the EASIEST WAYS TO DO IT. <BR>
<BR>
Okay here's what you do you bind at east freeport(although i binded myself everywhere i went). <BR>
1. Honeyjum<BR>
First you get 3 honeycombs. Four places you can get it from is misty thicket, kithicor woods(not recommened), or east commons, and west commons(i'm not sure. but i think you can). Then you go to Riverale. Find Kizzie Wintopp inside an undergournd hut. I suggest for the better to make srue it doesn't fail(just in case), to cast illusion gnome or halfling(it tink you can do dwarf too but i did gnome) and alliance on kizzie. Giver her the 3 honeycombs and 30 gold coins. <BR>
2. Erud's Tonic. Get a TP to Toxxulia. Go to Erudin. Now go to Blue Hawk(i tthink thats the name) tavern or something and buy Innorku's Kiss of Death and go to top of libraby and give it to SInnikin Highbrow. Then hop on the boat to Qeynos. <BR>
3. Koalindi Fish. I know a way to do it WITHOUT REDUCING FACTION, but better if you have Sow, a lot better. Now at Qeynos head to Surefall. Go to the Druids guild adn talk to the person on your left. Hail him and then talk and talk till you get the flask of nitrates. Then got o Ak'anon. Go to bottom of the Zoo, and I mean bottom. When you see the tiger display jump over the litlte ledge and then fall a few feet. Go to the gnome dude and cast illusion:gnome and alliance. He is the ONLY ONE there mind you so dont' give it to one of the other dudes that look teh same. He has a REAL NAME. GIve him flask of nitarate he'll give you a regurtonic. Take the regurtonic to West Karana. Give it to Frostbite in Barb Camp. (I cast illusion:barbarian even though it prob doesn't matter). He'll give you Koalindi Fish. <BR>
4. Kiola Nut-If you are going to go to Ak'ANon thorugh the baot from Freeport STOP at the island and go to tavern. Buy the Kiola Nut form merchant. Take like 5 gold and you can afford it. Remember its the boat FROM FREEPORT TO BUTCHERBLOCK&gt; not the only way around. <BR>
<BR>
Now you got all teh 4 components take it to bartender at tavern at dock. He'll give you Compendium then you take it to Clurg in Oggok. I can not give you information about Clurg for my deity makes it so I CANNOT go to Oggok. Here is what you do about Deity Problem<BR>
<BR>
WIth someone you trust, do this trick: Give them one out of 2 of the tradable components. Turn 3 of them in and have him or her turn in fourth one. He or She will get the compendium and THEY can run to Oggok for you. I however did not get to ahve this work for somebody had already put in the Kiola Nut and I ended up with teh COmpendium. I am however in the process of doing it again. Thank YOu everyone. You can contact me on Morrole-Thule my character's name is Karynn. I'm a level 17 high elf enchanter who follows Erollsi. 
